    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-08-30T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-08-30T00:00:00-05:00" n="37"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d37">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">Roosevelt Papers: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Roosevelt</persName> to Prime
                        Minister <persName type="to">Churchill</persName>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d37fn1">Sent to the United States Naval Attaché London, via
                        Navy channels.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">top secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">priority</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-08-30">30 August
                            1944</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Number 610, personal and top secret, from the President for the Prime
                    Minister.</p>
                <p>Your 771.<note n="2" xml:id="d37fn2">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_23">p. 23</ref>.</note> I am
                    pleased that our final arrangements for <gloss target="#t_Octagon1">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Octagon</hi>
                    </gloss> will keep the number who will participate in the conference to the
                    Teheran level insofar as practicable.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
